---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Read our privacy policy and understand how we handle your data.">
  <section class="max-w-screen-lg mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8">1. Introduction</h2>
    <p>Welcome to our website. Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting any personal information you share with us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8">2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
      <li>Personal information (such as your name and email address) if you contact us directly.</li>
      <li>Non-personal data such as your IP address, browser type, and usage data through analytics tools.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
      <li>Improving and maintaining our website.</li>
      <li>Analyzing trends and gathering user statistics.</li>
      <li>Responding to inquiries or feedback.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8">4. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
    <p>We may use cookies to enhance your browsing experience. You can adjust your browser settings to refuse cookies.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>Our website may use third-party services such as analytics providers or content hosting services. These services may collect information about your interactions with our website.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8">6. Data Security</h2>
    <p>We implement security measures to protect your data, but no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8">7. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to request access, correction, or deletion of your personal data. Please contact us if you wish to exercise these rights.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8">8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8">9. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us through our website @ <a href="https://contact.tinkernerd.dev" target="_blank" title="Contact Nick" class="text-sm text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-200">Contact.Tinkernerd.dev</a>.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>

